          <li>Miete am 03.04.</li>
          <li>Strom am 05.04.</li>
          <li>Versicherung am 08.04.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="kpi-ranking-card">
        <div class="kpi-ranking-card__head">
          <span class="kpi-card__label">Top-Kategorien nach Ausgaben</span>
          <strong>April 2026</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="category-ranking">
          <div class="category-ranking__item">
            <div class="category-ranking__meta">
              <span>Wohnen</span>
              <strong>1.180,00 EUR</strong>
            </div>
